      <h1>
          <a href="/blog" id="blog-home"><span class="octicon octicon-home"></span></a><a href="/blog/1876-github-for-windows-now-supports-mentions" class=" blog-title">GitHub for Windows now supports @mentions</a>
      </h1>
    </div>
